%% Diagram 04 — Polimorfisme saat shape.hitung...
flowchart TD
    START([Pemanggilan di GeoProcessor.run]) --> P1[Variabel Geometri shape]
    P1 --> P2[shape.hitungLuas / Keliling / Volume / LuasPermukaan]
    P2 --> D1{Runtime: tipe objek di heap?}
